## Context

We need posibility to create new static websites without touching code of application.

## Decision

Headless cms [Cosmicjs](https://www.cosmicjs.com/) allow us to create new static pages and editing exisitng like "Terms and conditions".

## Consequences

Easy way to create and edit static pages

